</P>
<P>
1511 N. Main St., Orange 
</P>
<P>
(714) 974-6244 
</P>
<P>
Hours: 11:30 a.m. to 5 p.m. Monday-Friday; 9 a.m. to 5 p.m. Saturday and Sunday 
</P>
<P>
Prices: $4.50 to $4.75 a foot; fire-retarding $2.75 
</P>
<P>
Notes: 4 1/2-acre farm with 1,600 trees; customers may reserve trees for pickup 
later. Staff cuts and will tie to car; candy canes, greens available. 
</P>
<P>
