</P>
<P>
1550 N. Glassell St., Orange 
</P>
<P>
(714) 998-2621 
</P>
<P>
Hours: noon to 5 p.m., Wednesday-Friday; 9 a.m. to 5 p.m. Saturday and Sunday 
</P>
<P>
Prices: Sizes from 2 to 10 feet; prices $2 to $70; flocking $2 a foot 
</P>
<P>
Notes: Two-acre farm with 2,600 trees; customers may reserve trees for pickup 
later. Customer may cut or staff will do so and tie on car. Free branches, 
trimmings and $2-off coupons. A nonprofit organization. 
</P>
