</P>
<P>
Hours: noon to 5 p.m. Monday-Friday; 9 a.m. to 5 p.m. Saturday and Sunday 
</P>
<P>
Prices: Sizes from 3 1/2 to 13 feet; $5 to $6 a foot, fire-retarding $2.50 a 
foot; compressing and netting for $2.50 
</P>
<P>
Notes: 10-acre farm; customers may reserve trees for pickup later. Delivery 
available; fee based on tree size and distance. Live container trees. Free 
candy canes, baby trees for planting, coloring books, petting zoo and hay 
rides; photo corner for picture takers. 
</P>
<P>
SANTA'S FOREST-YORBA LINDA 
</P>
<P>
4501 Eureka Ave., Yorba Linda 
</P>
<P>
(714) 993-3542 
</P>
<P>
Hours: 8 a.m. to 5 p.m. seven days a week 
</P>
<P>
Prices: $5.50 a foot; flame-retarding $3 a foot; flocking $2 to $3 a foot 
</P>
<P>
Notes: Five-acre farm, 3,000 trees. Delivery available; fee based on tree size 
and distance. Customers may reserve trees and pick up later. Customer may cut 
or staff will do so; tree disposal bags available. 
</P>
